1 This act would prohibit the distribution, transfer, or possession of any material that depicts
2 a minor engaging in sexually explicit conduct, is obscene and lacks serious literary, artistic,
3 political, or scientific value with violators subject to imprisonment and fines ranging from two (2)
4 to fifteen (15) years and fines from one thousand dollars ($1,000) to five thousand dollars ($5,000).
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
